This restriction was applied previously because charter companies do not allow their boats to be operated after sundown. We are leaving this decision up to the charter companies.

The new certificate will not include this restriction. If you do not have plans to charter in Europe and the stated restriction is not an issue, please know that when you renew the certificate, the restriction of ‚Äúdaylight hours‚Äù will not be included¬ª
